Title: API: extension of downtime endpoints functionality
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1612190072
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

This werk introduces some changes to the downtime endpoints. The delete downtime
endpoint's params option is renamed to 'by_id' and the params type now offers
the option to select delete downtimes by their hostname and/or service descriptions.
